        "questionText":"SẮP XẾP DỮ LIỆU KIỂU OBJECT",
        "answer":"<p>C&oacute; nhi\u1EC1u d\u1EA1ng \u0111\u1ED1i t\u01B0\u1EE3ng (object) kh&ocirc;ng th\u1EC3 tr\u1EF1c ti\u1EBFp s\u1EAFp x\u1EBFp, v&iacute; d\u1EE5 s\u1EAFp x\u1EBFp c&aacute;c \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng tr&ograve;n theo k&iacute;ch th\u01B0\u1EDBc.<br \/>\u0110\u1EA7u ti&ecirc;n, s\u1EBD ph\u1EA3i l\u01B0\u1EE3ng h&oacute;a nh\u1EEFng h&igrave;nh tr&ograve;n \u0111&oacute;, &aacute;nh x\u1EA1 th&agrave;nh nh\u1EEFng ch\u1EC9 s\u1ED1 c&oacute; th\u1EC3 s\u1EAFp x\u1EBFp \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c (int, float&hellip;), v&iacute; d\u1EE5<br \/>\u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng tr&ograve;n c&agrave;ng l\u1EDBn th&igrave; b&aacute;n k&iacute;nh c\u0169ng l\u1EDBn.<br \/>Sau \u0111&oacute;, c&aacute;c \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng tr&ograve;n n&agrave;y s\u1EBD \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c s\u1EAFp x\u1EBFp theo b&aacute;n k&iacute;nh (c\u0169ng c&oacute; th\u1EC3 theo chu vi, \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng k&iacute;nh, di\u1EC7n t&iacute;ch h&igrave;nh tr&ograve;n).<br \/>N&oacute;i chung, c&aacute;c b\u01B0\u1EDBc s\u1EAFp x\u1EBFp \u0111\u1ED1i v\u1EDBi object nh\u01B0 sau:<br \/>\u25CF L\u01B0\u1EE3ng h&oacute;a object theo m\u1EE5c \u0111&iacute;ch s\u1EAFp x\u1EBFp, trong \u0111&oacute; m\u1ED9t object s\u1EBD c&oacute; nhi\u1EC1u c&aacute;ch l\u01B0\u1EE3ng h&oacute;a kh&aacute;c nhau, v&iacute; d\u1EE5 nh\u01B0<br \/>c&aacute;c \u0111a gi&aacute;c c&oacute; th\u1EC3 s\u1EAFp x\u1EBFp theo s\u1ED1 c\u1EA1nh, s\u1ED1 g&oacute;c ho\u1EB7c di\u1EC7n t&iacute;ch&hellip; (m\u1ED9t \u0111a gi&aacute;c c&oacute; di\u1EC7n t&iacute;ch l\u1EDBn h\u01A1n ch\u01B0a ch\u1EAFc \u0111&atilde;<br \/>c&oacute; nhi\u1EC1u s\u1ED1 c\u1EA1nh h\u01A1n).<br \/>\u25CF S\u1EAFp x\u1EBFp c&aacute;c object theo c&aacute;c ch\u1EC9 s\u1ED1 \u0111&atilde; \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c l\u01B0\u1EE3ng h&oacute;a (nh\u01B0 c&aacute;c b&agrave;i tr\u01B0\u1EDBc)<\/p>",
        
