        "answer":"<p>. Nh\u1EEFng d\u1EA1ng s\u1EED d\u1EE5ng c\u1EE7a Linked list<br \/>&bull; Danh s&aacute;ch li&ecirc;n k\u1EBFt \u0111\u01A1n (Single linked list): Ch\u1EC9 c&oacute; s\u1EF1 k\u1EBFt n\u1ED1i t\u1EEB ph\u1EA7n t\u1EED ph&iacute;a tr\u01B0\u1EDBc t\u1EDBi ph\u1EA7n t\u1EED ph&iacute;a sau.<br \/>&bull; Danh s&aacute;ch li&ecirc;n k\u1EBFt \u0111&ocirc;i(Double linked list): C&oacute; s\u1EF1 k\u1EBFt n\u1ED1i 2 chi\u1EC1u gi\u1EEFa ph\u1EA7n t\u1EED ph&iacute;a tr\u01B0\u1EDBc v\u1EDBi ph\u1EA7n t\u1EED ph&iacute;a sau<br \/>&bull; Danh s&aacute;ch li&ecirc;n k\u1EBFt v&ograve;ng (Circular Linked List): C&oacute; th&ecirc;m s\u1EF1 k\u1EBFt n\u1ED1i gi\u1EEFa 2 ph\u1EA7n t\u1EED \u0111\u1EA7u ti&ecirc;n v&agrave; ph\u1EA7n t\u1EED cu\u1ED1i c&ugrave;ng<br \/>\u0111\u1EC3 t\u1EA1o th&agrave;nh v&ograve;ng kh&eacute;p k&iacute;n.<\/p>",
        
